snippet.title: 4 Wheel Thunder Gameplay Arcade Outdoor Series 1 (Dreamcast)
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more game footage! https://www.youtube.com/user/TheMfarec

4 Wheel Thunder Gameplay Arcade Outdoor Series 1 (Far West,Canada,Corsica)

Player: MfaRec

Description:

4 Wheel Thunder is a racing game developed by Kalisto Entertainment and published by Midway Games. While the game had been in development for some time prior as a separate title, it was eventually decided to rebrand the game into Midway's Thunder series.  The game has been praised for its realistic graphics and fun gameplay, but criticized for its high difficulty level.

Platform: Sega Dreamcast
Release Date: May 4, 2000
